        <Parent_String>Jin (Six Dynasties, culture, style, and period) [300018398], Six Dynasties [300264898], Southern and Northern Dynasties [300264899], Chinese dynastic styles and periods [300018353], Chinese (culture or style) [300018322], East Asian [300018321], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
